{{see|Swede}}
==English==
===Etymology===
Identical to ''[[Swede]]''.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/swi:d/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# (''mainly UK'') The fleshy root of a variety of [[rape]], ''Brassica napus'', similar to a large kind of [[turnip]], grown as a vegetable.
# The plant from which this is obtained.
# (''Scotland'') The [[turnip]].

====Synonyms====
*(''plant''): [[rutabaga]] (''US, Canada'') 
*(''vegetable''): [[rutabaga]] (''US, Canada'')

